description: Removes one or more tags from a signaling channel. In the request, specify only a tag key or keys; don't specify the value. If you specify a tag key that does not exist, it's ignored.

parameters.name: ResourceARN
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the signaling channel from which you want to remove tags.

parameters.name: TagKeyList
parameters.description: A list of the keys of the tags that you want to remove. (string) ---
